\c 123
\s Umkhuleko wokucela isihawu
\d Ingoma yokwenyuka
\p
\v 1 Ngiyaphakamisela kuwe amehlo ami\x + Hlab. 121.1. Hlab. 25.15. 141.8.\x*, wena ohlezi emazulwini\x + Hlab. 2.4. Hlab. 11.4.\x*.
\v 2 Khangela, njengalokhu amehlo ezinceku engasesandleni senkosi yazo, njengamehlo encekukazi engasesandleni senkosikazi yayo, ngokunjalo amehlo ethu angaseN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wethu, ize ibe lesihawu kithi.
\p
\v 3 Woba lesihawu kithi, N\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 4.1.\x*\nd*, woba lesihawu kithi\x + Hlab. 4.1.\x*, ngoba sigcwele kakhulu\x + Hlab. 120.6. Hlab. 129.1.\x* yikudelelwa\x + Neh. 4.4.\x*.
\v 4 Umphefumulo wethu ugcwele kakhulu yikukloloda\x + Neh. 2.19.\x* kwabonwabileyo\x + Amos 6.1.\x*, yikudelela kwabazigqajayo\x + Neh. 4.4.\x*.
